Pikakabat Ya Salita is a dictionary that aims to help its users gain extensiveand basic knowledge of the Pangasinan dialect. It also aims to share Pangasinan\'s history through trivia. Pikakabat Ya Salita wants to emphasize how lovely the town of Pangasinan is.
